Kusalattika
Paccayavāra
Paccayānulomapaccanīya
Aññamaññaduka
Tika
593Aññamaññapaccayā hetupaccayā naārammaṇe ekaṃ, naadhipatiyā satta, naanantare ekaṃ, nasamanantare ekaṃ, naupanissaye ekaṃ, napurejāte tīṇi, napacchājāte satta, naāsevane satta, nakamme satta, navipāke satta, nasampayutte ekaṃ, navippayutte tīṇi, nonatthiyā ekaṃ, novigate ekaṃ.
